text: Baygildino () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Baygildinsky Selsoviet, Nurimanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 432 as of 2010. There are 12 streets. == Geography == It is located 30 km from Krasnaya Gorka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Nurimanovsky District
title: Baygildino
